title: Pacific duo advances to quarterfinals
text: Pacific duo advances to quarterfinals Comment Posted Oct. 26, 2015 at 12:01 AM By The Record Posted Oct. 26, 2015 at 12:01 AM » Social News The Record Sem Verbeek and Miguel Diaz had a nice run at the 2015 USTA/ITA Northwest Regional Championships in Seattle. Unfortunately for the doubles pair from University of the Pacific, it came to an end in the quarterfinals. Verbeek and Diaz were defeated in the final eight by Nolan Paige and Maciek Romanowicz of Stanford 8-3 Sunday in Seattle. The Tigers duo beat Washington’s Rishabh Raman and Enzo Sommer 8-4 Saturday to get to the quarterfinals. By The Record
